    "description": {
      "zh": "用于替换 HK417 标准枪托的 E2 可伸缩枪托。采用高质量尼龙纤维材质打造，配有可旋转调节高度的橡胶托腮板，两边均设有枪带挂点，便于双手操作。可安装在 HK417/G28 武器系统的缓冲管上，由 HK 公司设计制造。",
      "en": "The E2 telescopic stock is designed as a replacement for standard HK417 stocks. Made of high-grade nylon fiber with a twist-off rubber butt pad and an ambidextrous sling attachment point. Can be installed on HK417/G28 weapon system buffer tubes. Manufactured by Heckler & Koch."
